snippet.title: Jawbreaker for the Apple II
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

Atari 8-bit family
(The Atari 2600 game is NOT like this one!)


Game description:

A clone of Pac-Man, where you as jaws must collect all points and escape lethal heads. There are also magical points to break heads by your jaws during some time. You have to collect the points, magical items, and progress from level to level.


What I think:

Can't reach Pac-Man, but it is a fun game nonetheless. 

But sometimes you don't have really control over your character and\or move to fast.
